ement,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of El-Islám; (TA;) and of anything. (S.) ―         -b3-  The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "whiteness"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of the teeth; and the ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "first that appears"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] of them. (K.) ―         -b4-  (assumed tropical:)  The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "head"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "app."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "when first appearing"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] of a plant. (TA.) ―         -b5-  (assumed tropical:)  [The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sight,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "spectacle,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "whatever appears to one,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of light, or daybreak: you say thereof,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "badato gur~atuhu", "text_ar": "بَدَتْ غُرَّتُهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The sight,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "spectacle, thereof appeared"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (K.) ―         -b6-  (assumed tropical:)  The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "aspect"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of the new moon: (K:) because of its whiteness: (TA:) or the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "phasis"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of the moon"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in the first night of the month"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "hl", "text_ar": "هل"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) ―         -b7-  (assumed tropical:)  The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "face"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of a man: (K:) or his"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "aspect;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "syn."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "TaloEap", "text_ar": "طَلْعَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) ―         -b8-  (assumed tropical:)  [And The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "forehead"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of a man. So used, as opposed to"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qafFA", "text_ar": "قَفًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in the Life of Teemoor, 170, ed. Mang., cited by Freytag; and so used in the present day; but whether in classical times I know not.] ―         -b9-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taTowiylu Algur~api", "text_ar": "تَطْوِيلُ الغُرَّةِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". in performing the ablution termed"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "waDuwo'", "text_ar": "وَضُوْء"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", means (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The washing of the fore part of the head with the face, and the washing of the side of the neck:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or, as some say"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the washing of somewhat of the fore arm and of the shank with the hand and the foot."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb) ―         -b10-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gur~ahN", "text_ar": "غُرَّهٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "also signifies (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A noble,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "an eminent man,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a chief,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "lord,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S,) of a people (S, K:) pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gurarN", "text_ar": "غُرَرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S.) ―         -b11-  And (tropical:)  The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "best."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K.)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and chiefest,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA,) of goods. or household furniture: (K:) pl. as above: (TA:) the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "best"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of anything: (S:) the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "best,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "most precious and excellent,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Aboo-Sa'eed,) of property ; as, for instance,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a horse,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "an excellent camel,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Aboo-Sa'eed, Mgh.) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "camels,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a male slave."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Aboo-Sa'eed. S. Mgh, Msb, K.) and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a female slave,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Msb, K,) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a clever female slave:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Aboo-Sa'eed, Mgh:) its application to a slave, male or female, [among articles of property,] is most common. (TA.) It has this last signification (a male or female slave) in a trad. in which it relates to the compensation for the destroying of a child in the womb: (TA:) as though this term were applied, by a synecdoche, to the whole person; (S;) the word properly signifying the “ face; ” in like manner as the terms"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "raqabapN", "text_ar": "رَقَبَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "raA^osN", "text_ar": "رَاْسٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "are employed: (Mgh:) Aboo-'Amr Ibn-El-Alà is related to have said that it there means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a white male slave"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a white female slave:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "but this is not a condition accord. to the doctors of practical law; for they hold the term to mean"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a male"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "female slave whose price amounts to the tenth part of the whole price of blood:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(IAth:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to the twentieth part thereof:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, T:) or it means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a slave of the best sort."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh.) The Rájiz says,"},